@Intervue.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Upload CV (PDF)
# Use Swagger UI or curl for multipart/form-data upload
# POST {{Intervue.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/cv/upload

### Parse CV
POST {{Intervue.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/cv/parse
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cvProfileId": "REPLACE_WITH_CV_ID"
}

### Start Interview
POST {{Intervue.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/interview/start
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cvProfileId": "REPLACE_WITH_CV_ID"
}

### Send Message
POST {{Intervue.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/interview/message
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interviewId": "REPLACE_WITH_INTERVIEW_ID",
  "content": "Your answer here..."
}

### Generate Feedback
POST {{Intervue.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/interview/feedback
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "interviewId": "REPLACE_WITH_INTERVIEW_ID"
}

### Get Interview by ID
GET {{Intervue.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/interview/REPLACE_WITH_INTERVIEW_ID
Accept: application/json

###
